<div id="content" class="container_16">

  <div id="order_details" class="grid_16">

    <div class="s_order clearfix">
      <p class="s_status"><span class="s_999">Numero do Pedido:</span>
          <span class="s_secondary_color">
            <%=@order.id%>
          </span>
      </p>
      <span class="clear border_eee"></span>

      <dl class="grid_5 alpha clearfix">
        <dt>Cliente</dt>
        <dd><%=@order.customer.name%></dd>
        <dt>E-Mail</dt>
        <dd><%=@order.customer.email%></dd>
        <dt>Telefone</dt>
        <dd><%=@order.customer.telephone%></dd>
        <dt>Método de Entrega</dt>
        <dd>Cupon</dd>
      </dl>

      <span class="clear border_eee"></span>

      <h2>Produtos</h2>
      <table class="s_table" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
        <tbody><tr>
          <th>Produto</th>
          <th>Empresa</th>
          <th>Quantidade</th>
          <th>Valor Unitário</th>
          <th width="130">Valor Total</th>
        </tr>
        <%@order.line_items.each do |line_item|%>
            <tr>
              <td class="align_left">
                <strong><%=line_item.product.name%></strong>
              </td>
              <td><%=line_item.product.company.name%></td>
              <td><%=line_item.quantity%></td>
              <td><%=valor_formatado line_item.product.price%></td>
              <td><%=valor_formatado line_item.total_price%></td>
            </tr>
        <%end%>

        </tbody></table>

      <h2>Order History</h2>
      <table class="s_table" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
        <tbody><tr>
          <th>Date Added</th>
          <th>Status</th>
          <th>Comments</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>07/04/2011</td>
          <td>Canceled</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>07/04/2011</td>
          <td>Reversed</td>
          <td>Pellentesque et diam at orci convallis ultrices in nec eros! Duis sit amet felis vitae diam vehicula pretium. Morbi pulvinar elit et quam feugiat quis aliquet neque venenatis? Suspendisse nisi arcu; semper eget convallis id, hendrerit eu odio. Nunc leo metus, malesuada nec congue in, rutrum vel risus. Mauris cras amet.</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody></table>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="clear"></div>

</div>